# Lint denylist (template). Copy to `.lint-forbidden-terms` (git-ignored).
#
# Format: one term per line. `#` comments and blank lines ignored.
# Match: case-sensitive substring against src/, scripts/, CLAUDE.md, README.md,
# bounded by non-alphanumeric. Hits → ERROR (blocks commit).
#
# Add: real org/product/MCP/skill/plugin names tied to your environment.
# Skip: generic placeholders (server1, orgA, my-skill, type-a) and `ccsight`.
#
# Example (replace with real terms after copying):
# my-real-org
# internal-product-x
